title: The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
